Dit is KKNK en die feesterrein en dorp is gewolbom! Die fraai fiets na­by die hoek van Baron van Reedestraat en Voortrekkerweg is die han­de­werk van Deleze van der Walt. Die pilaar links voor die Bur­ger­sentrum is versier deur Bets Wilkinson. Sy het ook ou feesgid­se by haar versiering ingebring. Foto’s bo en onder: Tieneke Maritz <img class="alignnone wp-image-25042 size-full" src="https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke.jpg" alt="" width="850" height="1909" srcset="https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke.jpg 850w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke-134x300.jpg 134w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke-768x1725.jpg 768w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke-456x1024.jpg 456w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke-672x1509.jpg 672w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke-120x270.jpg 120w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.-Feesgidse-in-Bets-se-paal-Tieneke-480x1078.jpg 480w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /> Wolkuns op Oudtshoorn. Foto bo: Christine Schoeman Foto’s onder: Tieneke Maritz <img class="alignnone wp-image-25039 size-full" src="https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/21-Tieneke-bib.jpg" alt="" width="850" height="638" srcset="https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/21-Tieneke-bib.jpg 850w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/21-Tieneke-bib-300x225.jpg 300w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/21-Tieneke-bib-768x576.jpg 768w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/21-Tieneke-bib-672x504.jpg 672w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/21-Tieneke-bib-360x270.jpg 360w, https://diehoorn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/21-Tieneke-bib-480x360.jpg 480w" si